cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CVPR

The paper proposes a new convolutional neural network architecture for visual localization and odometry estimation, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) categories. The paper also introduces a novel loss function and utilizes multitask learning, which involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper evaluates its proposed method on various datasets, which is relevant to computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CVPR).
